Paul Dempsey  Shotgun Karaoke [EP - 2013]

Paul Dempsey has just released his limited edition covers collection, Shotgun Karaoke. The CD EP is available from JB HiFi & Sanity & record stores. The 11 track CD version includes the bonus track, Web in Front (Archers of Loaf), while the 10 track digital version is released simultaneously worldwide via iTunes.

Recorded in an evening on acoustic guitar in the same  spur- of -the- moment spirit in which they were originally performed, we are very excited to reveal the track list of songs that made the final cut;

Artist: Paul Dempsey
